2008-10-22  Henri Häkkinen  <henux@users.sourceforge.net>

	* about.c (show_about_box): Added about box functionality.
	* rssfeed.c (on_open_url): Opens URLs using 'xdg-open'.
	* rssfeed.c (parse_channel_element): Changes the title of the menu
	item according to the RSS feed's title.
	* src/Makefile.am: Added common.h and rssfeed.h to _SOURCES.
	Added GNU build system files.
	Versions 0.1 and 0.1.1.

